    rdfs:comment "Canonical entity IRI. Provider homepage + #this convention per SoftwareApplication priority ladder (no DBpedia/Wikidata entry). Individual model versions are identified by schema:version."@en ;
    schema:dateCreated "2026-05-28T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

